下story講支持就攞光環!<br />\n對唔對住612班義示!!!  食胡椒噴霧、食催淚彈、什至係食子彈呀！！！！ <br />\n自己係冷氣房share下，就話自己係支持香港，你哋班垃圾收唔收恥呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一齊呼籲香港KOL清晰表明立場去發聲！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">急！！需要大家幫手！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你好，<br />\n作為香港既KOL, 係應該做Key Opinion Leader應該做既事！<br />\n如果你是支持這次香港的抗爭運動，希望你能夠發揮不同角色的作用，係你既網絡平台上發聲！<br />\n<br />\n作歌既可以作歌，拍片既可以拍片，寫文既可以寫文。<br />\n但絕對唔係求其出個story, 影下地下，影下天空，就話自己緊張香港。<br />\n<br />\n亦希望你清楚表明自己的立場，不是食大茶飯講d唔講d, 而係真真正正講出你對引渡法既睇法！<br />\n<br />\n當你口說支持，但又沒有就著KOL的角色，在網絡平台沒有就香港的抗爭作出清晰的回應和表明立場，身為Key Opinion Leader, 你慚愧嗎？"},{"pid":"817efe0c442e2d26e0f363809a64c7837b9be590","tid":1225063,"uid":42578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:46:51.000Z","msg":"之前係fb見到支持修例遊行，有警犬跟住保護佢地，大約有十幾個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2150aab0086c8e71832bcd3df33d31c858253f9c","tid":1225063,"uid":72801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"我都諗咗好耐，反修例嘅呢幾日都出咗嚟，支持修例嘅又點解無遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8e6cf655937c3b94a25d0f152dd90277b38c63","tid":1225063,"uid":17209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"係就快，唔好等下個禮拜"},{"pid":"af3aee94a6ab4bb50fea115115e1a2121566abc7","tid":1225063,"uid":